WEBVTT

00:00:01.603 --> 00:00:04.178
(Beeps)

00:00:04.202 --> 00:00:05.917
[Countdown]

00:00:05.941 --> 00:00:07.318
(Clapboard claps)

00:00:08.317 --> 00:00:11.806
Ten years is a long time
for us humans on earth.

00:00:11.830 --> 00:00:14.441
Ten turns around the sun.

00:00:14.465 --> 00:00:16.996
When I was on the TED stage a decade ago,

00:00:17.020 --> 00:00:19.255
I talked about planetary boundaries

00:00:19.279 --> 00:00:24.126
that keep our planet in a state
that allowed humanity to prosper.

00:00:24.150 --> 00:00:27.256
The main point is that
once you transgress one,

00:00:27.280 --> 00:00:29.486
the risks start multiplying.

00:00:29.510 --> 00:00:32.416
The planetary boundaries
are all deeply connected,